    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <opener><dateline><date when="1916-07-07">July 7, 1916</dateline></date>
                    <salute>Dear <persName key="harriet_monroe">Harriet</persName>:</salute></opener> 
                <p>Here is the copy of <title key="1777" level="a">“1777”</title> for the <title key="newPoetryAnthology" level ="m">>Anthology</title>. Good luck to you and it!</p>
                <p>Still not word from <persName key="margaret_anderson">Margaret Anderson</persName>, and I am anxiously awaiting your answer in regard to that.</p>
                <p>I think <persName key="wallace_stevens">Wallace Stevens’</persName>play most interesting and certainly deserving of the prize. That man has a great deal of talent. What a pity he writes so little!</p> 
                <closer>Affectionately yours,</closer>
        </body>
